  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluate the safety and efficacy of Peginterferon alfa-2a following Entecavir compared with
      Peginterferon alfa-2a monotherapy in patient with HBeAg positive chronic hepatitis B.

        -  Increased HBeAg seroconversion rate

        -  Increased HBsAg loss rate

        -  To define the best treatment condition for chronic HBV hepatitis patients
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
