  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Chronic hepatitis B patients with HBeAg positive, HBsAg positive, HBV DNA &gt; 100,000
             copies/ml and anti-HBs negative, serum ALT exceeding 2 X ULN but less than 10 X ULN.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient infected concurrently with HCV, HDV and HIV or patient with a history of
             antiviral treatment for Hepatitis B or patient with hepatic decompensation.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
